name: CloverMix
description:
! For Tools, check out HERE!! !

CloverMix

V1.0:CloverMix is merge model of ChilloutMix, LOFI, DDosMix and DreamShaper.

V2.0:Update LOFI, recalibrate merge ratios and add RetMix.

V3.0:Add/Change several models and recalibrate merge ratios.

HuggingFace

Merge Source:

V1.0:(Chilloutmix-Ni-pruned-fp32-fix (0.5) + LOFI V2pre (0.5) Weighted Sum) (0.5) + (DDosMix_v2 (0.5) + DreamShaper 4 baked vae (0.5) Weighted Sum) (0.5) Weighted Sum

V2.0:((Chilloutmix-Ni-pruned-fp32-fix (0.5) + LOFI V2 (0.5) Weighted Sum) (0.55) + (DDosMix_v2 (0.6) + DreamShaper 4 baked vae (0.4) Weighted Sum) (0.45) Weighted Sum) (0.7) + RetMix (0.3)

V3.0:

Sum Twice, ChillyMix-V2 + midmix-v2.0 + AddictiveFuture_Realistic_SemiAsian-V1, rand_alpha(0.2, 0.6, 1529739 ) rand_beta(0.3, 0.55, 10739422) >> 1a

Sum Twice, X-FlareMix-Real + epiCRealism-pureEvolutionV2 + XtReMiXUltiMateMerge-v1.5, rand_alpha(0.2, 0.7, 2641499 ) rand_beta(0.2, 0.65, 638192) >> 1b

Weighted Sum, 1a + 1b, rand_alpha(0.3, 0.7, 662491) >> 2

Sum Twice, DDosMix-v2 + RealDos-v1 + C3-v1.09, rand_alpha(0.3, 0.6, 446381 ) rand_beta(0.15, 0.7, 916223) >> 1c

Sum Twice, DreamShaper-6.31baked + XXMix_9realistic-v4.0 + majicMIXrealistic-v6, rand_alpha(0.2, 0.6, 96451 ) rand_beta(0.3, 0.65, 174891) >> 1d

Sum Twice, 2 + 1c + 1d, rand_alpha(0.35, 0.75, 183964 ) rand_beta(0.3, 0.5, 18369) >> 3

Sum Twice, 3 + ElZipang + RetMix-v2.0, rand_alpha(0.1, 0.3, 94518762 ) rand_beta(0.1, 0.25, 856182) >> CloverMixV3

Recommended Settings:

  • Sampler: “DPM++ SDE Karras” recommended.

  • Steps: 20~

  • Clipskip: 1 or 2

  • CFG Scale: 7 or higher recommended.

  • VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned

Recommended Prompt:

Prompt : (8k, best quality, masterpiece:1.2), (realistic, photo-realistic:1.37), ultra-detailed,

Negative : (deformed,distorted,disfigured:1.3),poorly drawn,bad anatomy,wrong anatomy,extra limb,missing limb,noating limbs,(mutated hands and finger:1.4),disconnected limbs,mutabon,mutated,ugly,disgusting,blurry,amputation

Recommended Upscaler:

  • Upscaler: Latent(nearest-exact)

  • Denoising strength: 0.5 ~ 0.6

  • Hires steps: 20 ~

  • Upscale by: 1.5 ~

Recommended Embeds:

  • bad hands

  • Easy Negative

  • Easy Negative V2

  • Deep Negative

  • Pure Eros Face
